_sText:
This is a AK/Colt arena. 2 crows nests at the top of each spawn contain a buy zone for players to buy extra equipment. This map supports 32 players and downloads quickly. Feel free to use on public and clan servers. I would appreciate any input for improvements or new ideas, you can email me at Nalthador@hotmail.com or just leave a comment.

Happy Shooting!
 -Nalthador
